Do you want to hear
how tough it's been for me?

31
00:02:17,860 --> 00:02:18,800
Go on.

32
00:02:22,350 --> 00:02:23,390
We just opened

33
00:02:23,390 --> 00:02:25,720
a pastry shop together.

34
00:02:26,390 --> 00:02:27,950
(Careful Pastry)
Is it necessary for us

35
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:28,730
to act like we are

36
00:02:28,730 --> 00:02:29,820
having an affair every day?

37
00:02:30,020 --> 00:02:30,860
You know very well.

38
00:02:30,860 --> 00:02:31,900
If Zhenzhu finds out

39
00:02:31,900 --> 00:02:33,960
that I'm running
a small business outside...

40
00:02:34,390 --> 00:02:35,770
We have to be extra careful.

41
00:02:40,620 --> 00:02:41,770
Help me out.

42
00:02:45,020 --> 00:02:47,120
I don't get it.

43
00:02:47,230 --> 00:02:49,230
Isn't doing business a good thing?

44
00:02:49,230 --> 00:02:50,490
Why can't you get it?

45
00:02:50,740 --> 00:02:52,960
I'm a matrilocal husband.

46
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:54,280
Making money behind her back

47
