is punishable by death.

48
00:02:55,620 --> 00:02:57,210
Why don't you just tell her?

49
00:02:58,070 --> 00:02:59,210
If I tell her,

50
00:03:00,140 --> 00:03:01,540
would there even be a share for me?

51
