52
00:03:03,070 --> 00:03:04,010
I can't do this.

53
00:03:04,900 --> 00:03:05,960
I'm really leaving.

54
00:03:06,350 --> 00:03:07,270
I really can't.

55
00:03:07,270 --> 00:03:08,820
I still need to buy a few more things.

56
00:03:08,830 --> 00:03:10,510
I'll sort it out and let you know.

57
00:03:10,510 --> 00:03:12,230
Hurry up. Don't delay the opening.

58
00:03:12,230 --> 00:03:14,120
We need more things?

59
00:03:14,460 --> 00:03:15,520
Of course.

60
00:03:15,670 --> 00:03:17,340
Do you think opening a shop
is that easy?

61
00:03:17,900 --> 00:03:19,280
But 200 wen for this?

62
00:03:19,390 --> 00:03:20,400
It's too expensive.

63
00:03:21,460 --> 00:03:22,880
But it's an imitation of a bracelet

64
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:24,190
worth 200 taels of silver.

65
00:03:24,670 --> 00:03:26,580
It's about 20 taels of silver.

66
00:03:26,580 --> 00:03:28,110
- Twenty?
- Twenty.

67
00:03:28,110 --> 00:03:29,050
This won't do.

68
00:03:33,790 --> 00:03:35,170
Where else can I scrape some money?

69
00:03:35,830 --> 00:03:36,770
Scrape?

70
00:03:38,790 --> 00:03:39,730
Lin Donglin?

71
00:03:40,350 --> 00:03:41,290
Scrape?

72
00:03:44,790 --> 00:03:46,120
Sometimes,

73
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:48,770
(Careful Pastry)
I really admire you.

74
00:03:57,420 --> 00:03:59,460
(Careful Pastry)

75
00:04:04,110 --> 00:04:05,050
Did I see it wrong?

76
00:04:11,510 --> 00:04:12,450
Jiao'e,

77
00:04:13,020 --> 00:04:14,210
you look really pretty today.

78
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,260
When don't I look pretty?

79
00:04:16,260 --> 00:04:17,200
Yes, yes.

80
00:04:17,470 --> 00:04:19,600
Where are you going?

81
00:04:20,590 --> 00:04:22,900
Mother asked me to deliver
shark fin soup to Grandmother.

82
00:04:25,380 --> 00:04:26,770
Where did you buy this?

83
00:04:27,300 --> 00:04:28,300
What?

84
00:04:28,300 --> 00:04:29,720
It looks quite nice.

85
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,590
Is it tasty?

86
00:04:30,590 --> 00:04:31,470
Go buy it yourself.

87
00:04:31,470 --> 00:04:32,310
No, I just...

88
00:04:32,330 --> 00:04:33,360
Let me...

89
00:04:33,990 --> 00:04:34,930
Don't touch.

90
00:04:35,450 --> 00:04:36,840
I'm just asking where you bought it.

91
00:04:36,850 --> 00:04:37,710
What for?

92
00:04:37,710 --> 00:04:38,890
Why are you so stingy?

93
00:04:39,110 --> 00:04:40,050
Move aside.

94
00:04:43,030 --> 00:04:43,970
What are you two doing?

95
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:45,820
Nothing, dear.

96
00:04:45,820 --> 00:04:47,520
I'm just chatting with Jiao'e.

97
00:04:47,670 --> 00:04:48,510
Hurry up.

98
00:04:48,510 --> 00:04:49,520
The dishes will get cold.

99
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,420
Yes, yes.

100
00:04:50,420 --> 00:04:51,360
Yes, dear.

101
00:04:54,030 --> 00:04:54,970
I'll go first.

102
00:04:56,860 --> 00:04:57,840
Lin Donglin,

103
00:04:58,470 --> 00:04:59,520
why did you go

104
00:04:59,860 --> 00:05:01,250
to the South Market this morning?

105
00:05:02,940 --> 00:05:04,500
What are you talking about,

106
00:05:04,500 --> 00:05:05,440
Jiao'e?

107
00:05:06,910 --> 00:05:08,250
I saw you this morning

108
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:10,060
at the entrance

109
00:05:10,060 --> 00:05:11,000
of Sining House,

110
00:05:12,420 --> 00:05:15,550
intimate with a woman.

111
00:05:15,550 --> 00:05:16,940
You can't just make things up.

112
00:05:16,940 --> 00:05:17,990
What woman?

113
00:05:17,990 --> 00:05:18,910
You must have

114
00:05:18,910 --> 00:05:20,360
mistaken someone else for me.

115
00:05:21,110 --> 00:05:22,060
Dear.

116
00:05:22,060 --> 00:05:23,650
Alright, I'll go right now.

117
00:05:24,500 --> 00:05:26,350
I have to go, or Zhenzhu will get mad.

118
00:05:26,350 --> 00:05:27,520
Could you deliver it for me?

119
00:05:29,230 --> 00:05:30,210
Don't make things up.

120
00:05:34,590 --> 00:05:36,360
I wasn't sure before.

121
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:38,480
Lin Donglin,

122
00:05:38,860 --> 00:05:40,280
you're a matrilocal husband.

123
00:05:40,550 --> 00:05:42,040
How dare you have an affair!

124
00:05:43,670 --> 00:05:44,920
I'll surely deal with you.

125
00:05:51,350 --> 00:05:52,290
Look at this.

126
00:05:54,990 --> 00:05:57,330
Only 50 wen

127
00:05:58,350 --> 00:05:59,400
for so many green plums.

128
00:05:59,860 --> 00:06:00,860
Where did you find them?

129
00:06:00,860 --> 00:06:02,210
I look for the cheapest ones.

130
00:06:02,350 --> 00:06:04,010
Miss, if you're not satisfied,

131
00:06:04,230 --> 00:06:05,260
you can pay a little more.

132
00:06:05,260 --> 00:06:06,280
What do you mean?

133
00:06:06,620 --> 00:06:07,790
If there's nothing wrong

134
00:06:07,790 --> 00:06:08,790
with these,

135
00:06:08,790 --> 00:06:10,160
why are they so cheap?

136
00:06:10,470 --> 00:06:12,620
Come on. I ran into a fraud before.

137
00:06:12,620 --> 00:06:14,450
All the fruits I bought
were about to ripen.

138
00:06:14,500 --> 00:06:16,040
But if you're making green plum sauce,

139
00:06:16,550 --> 00:06:17,490
they're just right.

140
00:06:21,420 --> 00:06:22,740
Hurry up, move faster.

141
00:06:22,740 --> 00:06:23,940
Why are you rushing?

142
00:06:23,940 --> 00:06:25,530
All you do is rush, rush, rush.

143
00:06:25,710 --> 00:06:27,010
Pay up and move them.

144
00:06:27,350 --> 00:06:28,930
- I'll take them all.
- Okay.

145
00:06:31,820 --> 00:06:33,210
200 taels for a secret.

146
00:06:33,790 --> 00:06:34,730
Not expensive, right?

147
00:06:41,990 --> 00:06:43,030
Miss,

148
00:06:43,030 --> 00:06:44,480
are you going to buy it or not?

149
00:06:45,350 --> 00:06:47,040
I'll be able to afford
the real one soon.

150
00:06:58,230 --> 00:07:00,480
Could you be gentler?

151
00:07:00,620 --> 00:07:02,160
I already am being gentle.

152
00:07:03,350 --> 00:07:04,860
Can't you be more tender?

153
00:07:04,860 --> 00:07:06,330
How tender do you want me to be?

154
00:07:08,820 --> 00:07:10,770
This time, I won't let you slip away.

155
00:07:12,670 --> 00:07:14,330
A couple of adulterers...

156
00:07:22,990 --> 00:07:24,810
What are you two doing?

157
00:07:25,030 --> 00:07:26,720
Didn't I tell you to lock the door?

158
00:07:50,150 --> 00:07:51,280
Wow.

159
00:07:51,860 --> 00:07:53,570
The cake you made

160
00:07:53,820 --> 00:07:54,890
is actually quite good.

161
00:07:56,790 --> 00:07:57,790
So, you must keep

162
00:07:57,790 --> 00:07:59,010
our secret.

163
00:08:00,910 --> 00:08:03,670
Why are you making such a fuss

164
00:08:03,670 --> 00:08:04,740
over this?

165
00:08:04,740 --> 00:08:05,680
It's not worth it.

166
00:08:06,820 --> 00:08:08,500
So, just leave after you finish.

167
00:08:08,500 --> 00:08:09,440
Don't come back.

168
00:08:13,350 --> 00:08:14,260
How much money

169
00:08:14,260 --> 00:08:15,360
do you two make in a month?

170
00:08:16,860 --> 00:08:17,890
Not much.

171
00:08:18,060 --> 00:08:19,280
Then I'll take 20% every month.

172
00:08:19,420 --> 00:08:20,360
Is that too much?

173
00:08:20,620 --> 00:08:21,970
- You're...
- Come on.

174
00:08:27,470 --> 00:08:28,410
Who are you?

175
00:08:29,470 --> 00:08:30,590
And who are you?

176
00:08:30,590 --> 00:08:32,350
I'm the chief disciple of the master

177
00:08:32,350 --> 00:08:33,690
from Mifang Pastry in Suzhou.

178
00:08:35,070 --> 00:08:36,010
30% every month.

179
00:08:38,190 --> 00:08:39,170
You go in first.

180
00:08:39,310 --> 00:08:40,540
I'll handle it.

181
00:08:40,540 --> 00:08:41,480
I'll talk to her.

182
00:08:45,950 --> 00:08:46,960
What's wrong with you?

183
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:48,230
Go back now

184
00:08:48,230 --> 00:08:49,290
and attend to Grandmother.

185
00:08:49,660 --> 00:08:50,860
I'll give you a box

186
00:08:50,860 --> 00:08:52,110
of pastries every month.

187
00:08:52,110 --> 00:08:53,050
How about that?

188
00:08:54,070 --> 00:08:55,050
What do you take me for?

189
00:08:56,230 --> 00:08:57,880
I want money.

190
00:08:58,260 --> 00:08:59,860
The Old Lady will buy pastries.

191
00:08:59,860 --> 00:09:00,710
Yes.

192
00:09:00,710 --> 00:09:02,690
If you don't give me money,

193
00:09:09,710 --> 00:09:10,840
I'll go back

194
00:09:10,990 --> 00:09:13,600
and tell Zhenzhu.

195
00:09:13,860 --> 00:09:15,170
You can't be serious.

196
00:09:15,470 --> 00:09:16,960
Are you so short of money?

197
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:19,090
Doesn't Grandmother give you
a monthly salary?

198
00:09:20,190 --> 00:09:21,010
I'm not a maid.

199
00:09:21,010 --> 00:09:22,140
Where would I get a salary?

200
00:09:22,140 --> 00:09:23,950
Just admit you're a maid.

201
00:09:23,950 --> 00:09:24,750
I'm not a maid.

202
00:09:24,750 --> 00:09:25,650
Then you have no money.

203
00:09:25,650 --> 00:09:26,830
So, I'm getting it from you.

204
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,200
- I don't have money.
- Earn it.

205
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:30,570
Have you had enough of my respect?

206
00:09:30,860 --> 00:09:32,210
Calm down, calm down.

207
00:09:32,210 --> 00:09:33,360
Are you never going to stop?

208
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,230
Right?

209
00:09:34,230 --> 00:09:35,330
Where did you come from?

210
00:09:36,860 --> 00:09:37,710
I'll beat you!

211
00:09:37,710 --> 00:09:38,650
Stop.

212
00:09:40,110 --> 00:09:41,210
This is my last word.

213
00:09:41,350 --> 00:09:42,960
I'll cover for you at home.

214
00:09:43,140 --> 00:09:45,380
You two keep working hard.

215
00:09:45,380 --> 00:09:46,230
What we talked about.

216
00:09:46,230 --> 00:09:47,260
It's settled, okay?

217
00:09:47,260 --> 00:09:48,590
I'm leaving now. Goodbye.

218
00:09:48,590 --> 00:09:49,330
Jiao'e, Jiao'e.

219
00:09:49,340 --> 00:09:50,470
- Let's talk.
- Come back.

220
00:09:50,470 --> 00:09:51,450
Who is she?

221
00:09:51,660 --> 00:09:52,780
Is she never going to stop?

222
00:09:52,780 --> 00:09:54,020
She even told me to work hard.

223
00:09:54,020 --> 00:09:55,860
- Who does she think she is?
- She's a nobody.

224
00:09:55,860 --> 00:09:57,500
Are you crazy?

225
00:09:57,500 --> 00:09:58,680
What's wrong with her?

226
00:09:58,680 --> 00:10:00,230
She wants a share, and you just agree?

227
00:10:00,230 --> 00:10:01,430
Do you really agree?

228
00:10:01,430 --> 00:10:02,830
Listen, her 30%

229
00:10:02,830 --> 00:10:03,830
comes out of your 60%.

230
00:10:03,830 --> 00:10:05,030
It has nothing to do with me.

231
00:10:05,310 --> 00:10:06,250
No, I...

232
00:10:09,860 --> 00:10:12,000
If you get 40% and she gets 30%,

233
00:10:12,990 --> 00:10:14,530
you'll be the boss, right?

234
00:10:42,660 --> 00:10:43,600
Why are you here?

235
00:10:43,900 --> 00:10:45,230
I thought you'd be too busy alone,

236
00:10:45,230 --> 00:10:45,970
so I came to help.

237
00:10:46,660 --> 00:10:47,540
Thank you.

238
00:10:47,540 --> 00:10:49,140
I'm not that busy here.

239
00:10:49,140 --> 00:10:50,020
But the flowers here

240
00:10:50,020 --> 00:10:50,960
need changing.

241
00:10:51,830 --> 00:10:53,350
I also brought some pastries for you.

242
00:11:18,380 --> 00:11:19,330
What's this?

243
00:11:20,380 --> 00:11:22,170
Tree peony, the most noble

244
00:11:22,380 --> 00:11:23,320
of all flowers,

245
00:11:23,590 --> 00:11:24,980
is suitable for honey maintenance.

246
00:11:25,830 --> 00:11:28,810
Sweet and lasting.

247
00:11:32,020 --> 00:11:32,860
That's nice.

248
00:11:32,860 --> 00:11:34,720
Ruan Ling, what are you doing?

249
00:11:36,990 --> 00:11:37,930
We are

250
00:11:38,350 --> 00:11:39,290
arranging flowers.

251
00:11:41,860 --> 00:11:42,980
This is an herbaceous peony.

252
00:11:43,260 --> 00:11:44,200
I know.

253
00:11:44,710 --> 00:11:45,590
I mean,

254
00:11:48,110 --> 00:11:49,020
she's a tree peony.

255
00:11:49,020 --> 00:11:50,690
You're disgusting.

256
00:11:52,070 --> 00:11:53,210
Don't you have work to do?

257
00:11:53,590 --> 00:11:54,530
I'm working right now.

258
00:11:54,990 --> 00:11:56,120
What about the customers?

259
00:12:00,310 --> 00:12:01,250
Then I'll go and work.

260
00:12:09,780 --> 00:12:10,720
Please.

261
00:12:18,190 --> 00:12:20,090
Lady Shuangxi,
why are you here again?

262
00:12:20,660 --> 00:12:21,820
To keep an eye on him for you.

263
00:12:22,070 --> 00:12:23,720
It's dangerous here.

264
00:12:26,010 --> 00:12:27,070
Do you know how many losses

265
00:12:27,070 --> 00:12:28,840
you've suffered without realizing it?

266
00:12:29,860 --> 00:12:30,800
I'm not suffering.

267
00:12:39,830 --> 00:12:41,410
Did you hear what I said?

268
00:12:43,430 --> 00:12:44,370
Keep going.

269
00:12:46,780 --> 00:12:47,740
How about this?

270
00:12:47,740 --> 00:12:49,230
Let's go to the yamen right now

271
00:12:49,230 --> 00:12:50,840
and bring him to justice.

272
00:12:53,740 --> 00:12:55,880
Go quickly, go.

273
00:12:56,780 --> 00:12:58,500
We'll have lunch together at noon.

274
00:12:58,500 --> 00:12:59,500
Are we inviting him

275
00:12:59,500 --> 00:13:00,660
for lunch?

276
00:13:00,660 --> 00:13:01,840
It's fine if you don't come.

277
00:13:01,950 --> 00:13:03,470
Guiwei, you don't have to work.

278
00:13:03,470 --> 00:13:04,450
Stop bossing me around.

279
00:13:04,830 --> 00:13:06,540
I have nothing else to do right now.

280
00:13:06,540 --> 00:13:08,510
Don't you see the incense
hasn't been burned yet?

281
00:13:09,860 --> 00:13:10,800
I'll do it.

282
00:13:14,660 --> 00:13:15,600
Lady Shuangxi.

283
00:13:15,900 --> 00:13:16,880
Don't touch it.

284
00:13:46,710 --> 00:13:47,810
What are you doing with it?

285
