581
00:25:07,910 --> 00:25:09,250
We didn't talk about anything.

582
00:25:10,430 --> 00:25:11,370
Is that so?

583
00:25:14,020 --> 00:25:15,050
If you

584
00:25:15,740 --> 00:25:17,680
tell me now

585
00:25:18,260 --> 00:25:20,090
and explain everything,

586
00:25:20,410 --> 00:25:23,010
