590
00:25:36,950 --> 00:25:38,730
I'll throw you out.

591
00:25:41,060 --> 00:25:42,000
Dear.

592
00:25:42,430 --> 00:25:44,330
I'll go get your foot-washing water.

593
00:26:18,230 --> 00:26:19,100
What's this?

594
00:26:19,100 --> 00:26:20,040
It's for you.

595
00:26:20,430 --> 00:26:21,370
For me?

596
00:26:27,190 --> 00:26:28,290
Thank you, Shuangxi.

597
00:26:37,990 --> 00:26:39,090
How much is it?

598
00:26:39,470 --> 00:26:40,630
Just keep it.

599
00:26:40,630 --> 00:26:42,090
What I give must be the best.

600
00:26:42,340 --> 00:26:43,230
Yes.

601
00:26:43,230 --> 00:26:44,740
I was just asking

602
00:26:44,740 --> 00:26:46,110
out of curiosity.

603
00:26:46,430 --> 00:26:47,370
Ten taels.

604
00:26:48,820 --> 00:26:49,760
Ten taels?

605
00:26:52,430 --> 00:26:54,290
The shopkeeper
must be good at business.

606
00:26:56,340 --> 00:26:57,280
You don't like it?

607
00:26:57,870 --> 00:26:59,880
No, I like it. I like it very much.

608
00:27:00,150 --> 00:27:00,990
Really?

609
00:27:00,990 --> 00:27:01,970
Of course.

610
00:27:03,470 --> 00:27:04,470
But your expression

611
00:27:04,470 --> 00:27:05,840
doesn't show that you like it.

612
00:27:06,230 --> 00:27:07,230
Don't lie to me.

613
00:27:07,230 --> 00:27:08,740
How could I lie to you?

614
00:27:08,740 --> 00:27:09,970
I really like it.

615
00:27:11,710 --> 00:27:12,630
If you don't like it,

616
00:27:12,630 --> 00:27:13,670
you can tell me.

617
00:27:13,670 --> 00:27:14,630
I hope we can be honest

618
00:27:14,630 --> 00:27:15,770
with each other.

619
00:27:21,230 --> 00:27:22,680
Well, if I tell the truth,

620
00:27:23,020 --> 00:27:24,430
