621
00:27:24,430 --> 00:27:25,370
I won't get angry.

622
00:27:26,300 --> 00:27:27,240
You see, it's like this.

623
00:27:27,740 --> 00:27:29,150
First of all, you gave me the cup.

624
00:27:29,150 --> 00:27:30,330
I like it very much.

625
00:27:30,820 --> 00:27:31,760
Secondly,

626
00:27:32,190 --> 00:27:33,260
it's probably worth

627
00:27:33,260 --> 00:27:34,360
at most one tael.

628
00:27:34,470 --> 00:27:35,710
Really. Look at it.

629
00:27:35,710 --> 00:27:37,240
First, the color isn't quite right.

630
00:27:37,240 --> 00:27:39,120
The kiln temperature
likely wasn't high enough.

631
00:27:39,150 --> 00:27:40,190
It was supposed to be made

632
00:27:40,190 --> 00:27:41,630
