633
00:27:41,630 --> 00:27:43,360
but didn't you notice?
It's crooked here.

634
00:27:44,020 --> 00:27:45,490
So, I said the cup is worth one tael

635
00:27:45,740 --> 00:27:46,880
to spare your feelings.

636
00:27:50,190 --> 00:27:51,430
So, you don't like it after all.

637
00:27:52,060 --> 00:27:53,580
No. I really like it.

638
00:27:53,580 --> 00:27:54,530
Don't patronize me.

639
00:27:54,640 --> 00:27:55,630
I'm not patronizing you.

640
00:27:55,630 --> 00:27:57,020
Your expression is patronizing.

641
00:27:57,020 --> 00:27:58,990
I'm not patronizing you.

642
00:27:58,990 --> 00:28:00,470
We agreed at the beginning.

643
00:28:00,470 --> 00:28:01,730
You can't get angry, right?

644
00:28:02,130 --> 00:28:02,990
Am I angry?

645
00:28:02,990 --> 00:28:03,970
I'm not angry.

646
00:28:04,030 --> 00:28:05,470
I went all the way to buy you a gift.

647
