If it's not valuable, so be it.

648
00:28:06,690 --> 00:28:07,630
Why would I be angry?

649
00:28:07,740 --> 00:28:08,580
How can I be angry?

650
00:28:08,580 --> 00:28:09,870
No, look.

651
00:28:09,870 --> 00:28:12,470
You, you...

652
00:28:12,470 --> 00:28:14,510
I'm just talking
about the matter itself.

