654
00:28:16,500 --> 00:28:18,670
It really isn't worth that much.

655
00:28:18,670 --> 00:28:20,060
Now, you don't even pretend anymore,

656
00:28:20,060 --> 00:28:20,990
do you?

657
00:28:20,990 --> 00:28:22,470
No, I was pretending at first,

658
00:28:22,470 --> 00:28:24,230
but you forced me to tell the truth.

659
00:28:24,230 --> 00:28:25,530
I forced you?

660
00:28:26,070 --> 00:28:26,910
I was just asking.

661
00:28:26,910 --> 00:28:28,250
Does that mean I forced you?

662
00:28:28,390 --> 00:28:29,330
Alright, give it back.

663
00:28:29,870 --> 00:28:30,740
No, no.

664
