00:28:32,740 --> 00:28:34,120
Let's not make a fuss, shall we?

666
00:28:36,540 --> 00:28:37,480
Make a fuss?

667
00:28:38,020 --> 00:28:39,200
No, that's not what I meant.

668
00:28:39,270 --> 00:28:40,670
- Give it back.
- I didn't mean it.

669
00:28:40,670 --> 00:28:41,830
- I'm wrong.
- Give it back!

670
00:28:45,170 --> 00:28:46,060
I...

671
00:28:46,060 --> 00:28:47,160
I didn't mean to.

672
00:28:49,060 --> 00:28:51,670
How dare you do this
to Lady Shuangxi?

673
00:28:51,670 --> 00:28:52,610
I...

