00:28:53,430 --> 00:28:54,640
Did he bully you?

675
00:28:56,630 --> 00:28:57,570
Yes.

676
00:28:59,950 --> 00:29:01,600
Shuangxi, Shuangxi.

677
00:29:01,740 --> 00:29:02,580
You're done for.

678
00:29:02,620 --> 00:29:04,190
I've got you by the scruff of the neck.

679
00:29:04,190 --> 00:29:05,730
I've got you.

680
00:29:06,300 --> 00:29:08,050
Lady Shuangxi, report it.

681
00:29:22,950 --> 00:29:26,050
Life is all about business.

682
00:29:27,470 --> 00:29:32,090
The key to business is opportunity.

683
00:29:34,540 --> 00:29:35,570
Opportunity is

684
00:29:36,020 --> 00:29:38,440
for those who are prepared.

685
00:29:39,580 --> 00:29:41,290
So, who are the prepared ones?

686
00:29:45,430 --> 00:29:46,910
Those who are always ready

687
00:29:46,910 --> 00:29:48,680
to take a chance.

688
00:29:50,020 --> 00:29:50,960
Yes.

689
00:29:51,780 --> 00:29:52,720
So,

690
00:29:53,630 --> 00:29:54,640
my friends,

691
00:29:55,870 --> 00:29:56,810
are you ready

692
00:29:57,630 --> 00:29:59,260
to take a chance?

693
00:29:59,260 --> 00:30:00,500
After all that you've said,

694
00:30:00,500 --> 00:30:02,290
what business are you going
to take us into?

695
00:30:02,580 --> 00:30:03,520
Exactly.

696
00:30:05,190 --> 00:30:06,160
Careful.

697
00:30:07,870 --> 00:30:08,920
There's no one else here.

698
00:30:09,870 --> 00:30:10,710
I'm talking

699
00:30:10,710 --> 00:30:12,300
about the business we're going to do.

700
00:30:12,300 --> 00:30:14,970
The shop is called Careful Pastry.

701
00:30:16,870 --> 00:30:18,150
Careful Pastry?

702
00:30:18,150 --> 00:30:19,490
I've had it. It's delicious.

703
00:30:19,670 --> 00:30:20,710
Have you?

704
00:30:20,710 --> 00:30:21,710
So, how did you become

705
00:30:21,710 --> 00:30:22,970
the owner of Careful Pastry?

706
00:30:24,500 --> 00:30:25,640
I've got

707
