710
00:30:30,430 --> 00:30:31,740
Yes, if it's a loss,

711
00:30:31,740 --> 00:30:32,780
what about our money?

712
00:30:32,780 --> 00:30:33,720
Yes.

713
00:30:35,230 --> 00:30:36,250
To be honest,

714
00:30:36,430 --> 00:30:38,200
that's how business is.

715
00:30:38,430 --> 00:30:40,470
There's profit and loss.

716
00:30:40,470 --> 00:30:42,060
If it were a sure thing,

717
00:30:42,060 --> 00:30:43,160
why would I need you?

718
00:30:44,910 --> 00:30:46,190
- Right.
- That's the point.

719
00:30:46,190 --> 00:30:48,330
If you want to get rich,

720
00:30:48,710 --> 00:30:50,200
and you don't have the guts,

721
00:30:50,710 --> 00:30:52,290
then you'll be a maid for life.

722
00:30:56,060 --> 00:30:57,330
So, how much money do you need?

723
00:30:58,260 --> 00:30:59,770
Fifty taels is the limit.

724
00:31:00,100 --> 00:31:02,300
- Fifty?
- Fifty?

725
00:31:02,300 --> 00:31:03,340
Oh my God!

726
00:31:03,340 --> 00:31:04,260
But I won't take

727
00:31:04,260 --> 00:31:05,540
more than that.

728
00:31:05,540 --> 00:31:06,870
No matter how much more.

729
00:31:06,870 --> 00:31:08,600
Just 50 taels. Yes.

730
00:31:09,710 --> 00:31:10,710
Fifty.

731
00:31:10,710 --> 00:31:12,680
Fifty taels is too much.

732
00:31:13,630 --> 00:31:15,920
Our monthly salary isn't much.

733
00:31:18,580 --> 00:31:19,990
No, I've said it all.

734
00:31:19,990 --> 00:31:21,680
Why are you still hesitating?

735
00:31:21,950 --> 00:31:22,990
Let me ask you.

736
00:31:22,990 --> 00:31:24,250
How much is your monthly salary?

737
00:31:24,340 --> 00:31:25,360
What about 30 years later?

738
00:31:25,360 --> 00:31:26,730
When the Jings no longer need you,

739
00:31:26,730 --> 00:31:28,040
