00:32:49,780 --> 00:32:51,390
It's a small matter.

788
00:32:51,390 --> 00:32:52,440
Take your teeth back.

789
00:32:52,780 --> 00:32:55,470
Once our shop is up

790
00:32:55,470 --> 00:32:56,530
and running,

791
00:32:56,950 --> 00:32:58,740
we'll open one
in North Port, South Market,

792
00:32:58,740 --> 00:32:59,910
East Street, and West Alley.

793
00:33:00,020 --> 00:33:01,840
Once these shops are thriving,

794
00:33:02,020 --> 00:33:03,730
we'll go straight to Anning Prefecture.

795
00:33:03,750 --> 00:33:04,430
Yes, yes.

796
00:33:04,430 --> 00:33:06,220
Once we're established
in Anning Prefecture,

797
00:33:06,300 --> 00:33:07,700
we'll open shops in the Capital

798
00:33:07,740 --> 00:33:08,740
and Suzhou.

799
00:33:08,740 --> 00:33:09,630
By then,

800
00:33:09,630 --> 00:33:10,820
if the noble and the wealthy

801
00:33:10,820 --> 00:33:12,440
like our pastries,

802
00:33:12,820 --> 00:33:13,710
our pastries

803
00:33:13,710 --> 00:33:15,440
will become as renowned

804
00:33:15,670 --> 00:33:16,810
as Jinyu Tea.

805
00:33:17,230 --> 00:33:18,170
Yes.

806
00:33:18,340 --> 00:33:20,210
Great. It'll be passed down
through the ages.

807
00:33:20,870 --> 00:33:21,920
Speaking of which,

808
00:33:22,450 --> 00:33:23,540
it's all thanks to you two,

809
00:33:23,540 --> 00:33:24,490
