810
00:33:24,710 --> 00:33:25,780
so our shop can get off

811
00:33:25,780 --> 00:33:27,730
to such a smooth start.

812
00:33:35,260 --> 00:33:37,740
Thank you, thank you both.

813
00:33:37,740 --> 00:33:38,680
Don't thank me yet.

814
00:33:40,540 --> 00:33:41,840
Subordinates?

815
00:33:44,470 --> 00:33:45,630
When did we become

816
00:33:45,630 --> 00:33:47,770
