00:34:06,570 --> 00:34:07,630
(Careful Pastry)
Stop it.

830
00:34:07,630 --> 00:34:09,090
- Alright.
- Give me my money back!

831
00:34:48,270 --> 00:34:50,550
I'll have Lady Shuangxi
