00:35:06,500 --> 00:35:08,450
Shuangxi,

835
00:35:11,140 --> 00:35:12,080
I'm sorry.

836
00:35:14,950 --> 00:35:15,890
After that day,

837
00:35:16,580 --> 00:35:18,280
I reflected deeply.

838
00:35:19,540 --> 00:35:20,750
I focused on arguing with you

839
00:35:20,750 --> 00:35:21,930
